title: Trump vs. Biden: Who raised more in June?

markets.question: Trump vs. Biden: Who raised more in June?
markets.description:

The specific filings can be accessed via the following links: Biden's FEC filing at https://docquery.fec.gov/cgi-bin/forms/C00703975/sa and Trump's FEC filing at https://docquery.fec.gov/cgi-bin/forms/C00828541/DJTFP24.COM.
